title: Monster War
description:
The heroes of the Top Cow Universe face off against the deadliest foes of Dynamite Entertainment in a four-part story arc that will pit The Magdalena vs Dracula, Tomb Raider vs the Wolfmen, Witchblade vs Frankstein and The Darkness vs Mr. Hyde.

Written by Christopher Golden and Tom Sniegowski, and featuring the art of Joyce Chin and Vitor Ishimura.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
